e Brahman Brothers|Brahman Kei]], [[The Brahman Brothers|Brahman Shu]] and [[The Great Sasuke]]) defeated [[Ryuji Ito]] and Speed of Sounds ([[Tatsuhito Senga|Hercules Senga]] and [[Tsutomu Oosugi]]) |time6=11:04 |stip7=Singles match |match7=[[Daisuke Sekimoto]] defeated [[Takashi Sugiura]] |time7=18:52 |stip8=[[Professional wrestling match types#Hardcore-based variations|Glass Board and Kenzan Deathmatch]] for the [[BJW Deathmatch Heavyweight Championship]] |match8=[[Yuko Miyamoto]] (c) defeated [[Masashi Takeda (wrestler)|Masashi Takeda]] |time8=12:06 }}
