===Awards===
* Spanish ''[[Medalla Militar]]''{{sfn|Berger|1999|p=139}}
* [[Spanish Cross]] in Gold with Swords{{sfn|Berger|1999|p=139}}
* [[Wound Badge]] in Black{{sfn|Berger|1999|p=139}}
* [[Front Flying Clasp of the Luftwaffe|Front Flying Clasp of the ''Luftwaffe'']] in Gold with Pennant "1000"{{sfn|Berger|1999|p=139}}
* [[Combined Pilots-Observation Badge]]{{sfn|Berger|1999|p=139}}
* [[Iron Cross]] (1939)
** 2nd Class (26 September 1939){{sfn|Thomas|1997|p=317}}
** 1st Class (4 July 1940){{sfn|Thomas|1997|p=317}}
* [[Ehrenpokal der Luftwaffe|Honorary Cup of the ''Luftwaffe'']] (12 June 1941){{sfn|Obermaier|1989|p=31}}
* [[German Cross]] in Gold on 9 April 1942 as ''[[Hauptmann]]'' in the I./''Jagdgeschwader'' 77{{sfn|Patzwall|Scherzer|2001|p=204}}
* [[Knight's Cross of the Iron Cross with Oak Leaves and Swords]]
** Knight's Cross on 13 September 1940 as ''[[Oberleutnant]]'' and pilot in the I./''Jagdgeschwader'' 77{{sfn|Fellgiebel|2000|p=239}}{{sfn|Von Seemen|1976|p=177}}{{refn|According to Scherzer in the I.(J)/LG 2.{{sfn|Scherzer|2007|p=413}}|group="Note"}}
** 16th Oak Leaves on 27 June 1941 as ''Hauptmann'' and ''[[Gruppenkommandeur]]'' of the I./''Jagdgeschwader'' 77{{sfn|Scherzer|2007|p=413}}{{sfn|Fellgiebel|2000|p=54}}{{sfn|Von Seemen|1976|p=25}}
** 9th Swords on 24 April 1942 as ''Hauptmann'' and ''Gruppenkommandeur'' of the ''I./''Jagdgeschwader'' 77{{sfn|Scherzer|2007|p=413}}{{sfn|Fellgiebel|2000|p=39}}{{sfn|Von Seemen|1976|p=14}}
* Six named references in the ''[[Wehrmachtbericht]]'' (27 June 1941, 26 March 1942, 20 April 1942, 21 April 1942, 23 April 1942){{sfn|The Wehrmacht Reports 1939–1945 Volume 1|p=591}}{{sfn|The Wehrmacht Reports 1939–1945 Volume 2|pp=67, 73, 91–92, 94}}

