et British PM Theresa May for an hour and 15 minutes on the sideline of UNGA|url=https://twitter.com/ragipsoylu/status/778274410344148992|website=www.twitter.com|publisher=@ragipsoylu|accessdate=20 September 2016|date=20 September 2016}}</ref> She also attended a reception for American companies operating in the United Kingdom.<ref>{{cite news|last1=Dominiczak|first1=Peter|title=May to meet US business leaders including IBM and Goldman Sachs bosses to thwart post-Brexit plans to move Euro headquarters from UK|url=https://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/2016/09/19/theresa-may-meets-top-us-business-leaders-to-thwart-post-brexit/|accessdate=19 September 2016|work=[[The Daily Telegraph]]|issue=50,178|publisher=[[Telegraph Media Group]]|date=19 September 2016}}</ref>
