| {{flag|Switzerland}} 
| [[Davos]]
| {{sort|2017-01-19|19 January}}
| May addressed and met with business leaders at the [[World Economic Forum]] in Davos, reassuring them of their relationship amid her government's Brexit plans.<ref>{{cite news|title=Theresa May set to reassure business leaders in Davos|url=http://www.itv.com/news/2017-01-19/theresa-may-set-to-reassure-business-leaders-in-davos/|accessdate=27 January 2017|publisher=[[ITV News]]|date=19 January 2017}}</ref>
